import React from 'react'
import {AboutSection,
        AboutContainer} from './AboutElements'

import tux from '../../images/tux.png'

function index() {
    return (
        <AboutSection>
            <AboutContainer>
                <AboutTitle>Croco-OS Team:</AboutTitle>
                <AboutTeam>
                    <Member>
                        <MemberName>GiacoLenzo2109</MemberName>
                        <MemberImg src={tux}/>
                    </Member>
                </AboutTeam>
            </AboutContainer>
        </AboutSection>
    )
}

export default index
